19#ifndef _PROPERNAME_H
20#define _PROPERNAME_H
21
22
23#ifdef __cplusplus
24extern "C" {
25#endif
26
27/* Return the localization of NAME. NAME is written in ASCII. */
28extern const char * proper_name (const char *name);
29
30/* Return the localization of a name whose original writing is not ASCII.
31 NAME_UTF8 is the real name, written in UTF-8 with octal or hexadecimal
32 escape sequences. NAME_ASCII is a fallback written only with ASCII
33 characters. */
34extern const char * proper_name_utf8 (const char *name_ascii,
35 const char *name_utf8);
36
37#ifdef __cplusplus
38}
39#endif
40
41
42#endif /* _PROPERNAME_H */
